snippet.title: TeslaTech
snippet.description:
Albert Einstein was asked' "How does it feel the be the smartest man in the world?" and he answered; "I don't know, ask Nikola Tesla."

This channel is about the science that Nikola Tesla started and modern day inventors researching his inventions and networking their ideas.
